name: Nextlist
tagline: Easy Nextweb synchronization for jQuery UI Sortable
body:
Nexlist is a jQuery plug-in that makes it incredibly easy to make your jQuery UI Sortable lists synchronized with Nextweb. It was designed to be easy to use and flexible.

For code, documentation, demos and more, go to the [GitHub repository](https://github.com/kishang/nextlist).
